00:46:31,889 --> 00:46:35,359
Come on!  Come on!
Come on!  Come on!

601
00:46:35,359 --> 00:46:38,395
- Swim!
- Dad, grab this!

602
00:46:38,395 --> 00:46:40,563
Swim, that's right!

603
00:46:44,034 --> 00:46:47,937
Don't look back!
Swim!  Come on!

604
00:46:49,239 --> 00:46:52,709
