sir.

623
00:48:11,622 --> 00:48:13,790
- What?
- Your language.

624
00:48:15,525 --> 00:48:18,127
- I said Kafka.
- I heard what you said.

625
00:48:18,128 --> 00:48:19,429
There's a lady present.

626
00:48:19,429 --> 00:48:21,597
